name: SoleilRadio
0:

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: soleil radio
des:
Listen to the Channel Islands' greatest songs all day long with Soleil Radio.

Simply say ‘Alexa, play Soleil Radio’ or ‘Alexa, open Soleil Radio' to start listening.

At any time you can stop listening to the station by saying, ‘Alexa, stop’.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
